sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor App as App (ssh / curl)
  participant LIBC as libc / getaddrinfo
  participant RC as /etc/resolv.conf
  participant NSCD as NSC DNS<br/>127.0.0.54:53 (UDP, 默认)
  participant MAP as DnsRecords<br/>Arc RwLock HashMap
  participant UP as Upstream<br/>1.1.1.1:53

  App->>LIBC: getaddrinfo("ssh.office.n.ns")
  LIBC->>RC: read nameserver
  RC-->>LIBC: nameserver 127.0.0.54
  LIBC->>NSCD: DNS query (ID=0xABCD, QTYPE=A)<br/>QNAME = ssh.office.n.ns

  NSCD->>NSCD: parse_question<br/>domain = "ssh.office.n.ns" qtype=1
  NSCD->>MAP: read().get("ssh.office.n.ns")

  alt 命中
    MAP-->>NSCD: 127.11.0.1
    NSCD->>NSCD: build_a_response<br/>flags=0x8400 | RD_bit<br/>TTL=60 RDATA=127.11.0.1
    NSCD-->>LIBC: DNS response (ID=0xABCD, A 127.11.0.1)
  else miss (qtype≠A, 或 domain 未登记)
    MAP-->>NSCD: None
    NSCD->>UP: 转发原始 query<br/>(UdpSocket::bind 0.0.0.0:0 → send_to 1.1.1.1:53)
    UP-->>NSCD: upstream 响应
    alt 2 秒内返回
      NSCD-->>LIBC: 透传上游响应
    else 超时
      NSCD--xLIBC: drop (debug log)
    end
  end

  LIBC-->>App: 127.11.0.1

  App->>App: TCP connect 127.11.0.1:22<br/>→ 打中 NSC VIP listener (proxy.rs)
  Note over App,UP: 对于 OFFICE.N.NS 等大小写变体，<br/>handle_query 用 to_lowercase() 匹配
